### 🧪 Microservices Communication HTTP Test Client

# Konfigurasi Environment
@hostname = localhost
@port = 5000
@host = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}

###
# 1. Panggil Product Service Internal Langsung (Port yang sama untuk demo)
GET {{host}}/api/products/1

###

# 2. Buat Order Baru (Order Service memanggil Product Service via Resilient HTTP)
# Skenario: Produk ada. Response 201 Created & Event ter-publish.
POST {{host}}/api/orders?productId=1&quantity=3

###

# 3. Buat Order Baru (Produk tidak terdaftar)
# Skenario: Product Service return 404. Order Service return 400 Bad Request.
POST {{host}}/api/orders?productId=99&quantity=1
